Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.29,0:01:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 差不多快到达布利斯了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.10,0:01:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,做梦了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.94,0:01:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 梦到那家伙了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.43,0:02:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,终于到了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.03,0:02:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.22,0:02:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,师父要是不在家就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.62,0:02:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.37,0:02:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,您…您好
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎啊 长大了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,会…会变矮
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…我是阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,久疏问候了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.89,0:02:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,长大了好多啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.63,0:02:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,变成铠甲之身以后第一次被摸摸头
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,伊兹密 艾尔利克家的小鬼们来了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.84,0:02:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,能下床吗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.41,0:02:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 今天感觉还好
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,原来不舒服正躺着呢
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,身体还没好起来啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这个笨徒弟
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.40,0:03:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你沦为军方走狗了？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,师父 那个…这个是…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.09,0:03:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔 你长这么高了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,师父倒是没什么变…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,锻炼得还不够
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,您不是身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.60,0:03:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,胡说八道 还不是因为你们来了我才…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太勉强自己啦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.23,0:03:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,让你担心了 老公
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,关于贤者之石我没什么造诣
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为没兴趣
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.92,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,以前在中央市
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不是见过一个很了解贤者之石的炼金术师吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.72,0:04:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得名字叫…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.68,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.32,0:04:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他还活着啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.77,0:04:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我们的父亲
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个以前就离家出走的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那个混蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.91,0:04:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲就是因为那种人才死的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为那种人…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这么早起来
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔说要尿尿
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏你照顾阿尔啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 爱德
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 爸爸呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.61,0:05:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,出门去了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.95,0:05:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,几时回来呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,咯吱咯吱咯吱
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.47,0:05:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,咯吱咯吱咯吱
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.36,0:05:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就会回来的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.59,0:05:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.73,0:06:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.88,0:06:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.57,0:06:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.99,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 关于贤者之石爸爸有没有提到什么
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.11,0:06:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,说是长年的愿望就快实现了 很开心的样子
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.76,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,吃饭去
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.16,0:06:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔不吃吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.90,0:06:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 我在火车上吃得很饱了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.36,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 阿尔
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.65,0:06:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在拉修瓦雷还看到小孩子的出生呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对对 师父
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.93,0:07:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还帮忙接生呢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.12,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 那根本就不算帮忙啦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.39,0:07:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一家人齐心协力 母亲也非常拼命
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.07,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人是在大家的祝福之下诞生的呀
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 你们也是这样获得了生命
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要为自己的生命感到骄傲
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.89,0:07:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,师父真是一点也没变呢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.25,0:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 和当年一模一样
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,再多拿点沙包来
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.72,0:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,堤坝要垮了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,决堤了 快往高处逃啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 你看
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 危险啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.31,0:08:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这样应该能撑一段时间了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你是什么人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.76,0:08:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,正巧路过的主妇
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,请收我们为徒吧 阿姨
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.27,0:09:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,求您了 阿姨
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.92,0:09:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨耳背没听清
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.49,0:09:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你们再说一遍？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,刚…刚才那句话收回
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请收我们为徒吧 大姐姐
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不收徒弟的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.54,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我还在旅行呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,求求您 收我们为徒吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.05,0:09:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们父母批准了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.60,0:09:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…他们没有父母的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就怕这种的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩想办法生存下来吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.08,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这是试修行
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,能通过就进入正式修行
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,试修行阶段禁止使用炼金术
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,「一即全 全即一」
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一个月内想出这句话的解答
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.13,0:10:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,答不出来就送回里森堡哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.07,0:10:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,闪了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.09,0:10:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}这算啥啊～啥啊～
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好想睡床上啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这算哪门子炼金术修行啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.68,0:10:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子好饿…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没问题吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.53,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,实践出真知嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想要深入了解炼金术的精髓
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那个方法最管用
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.13,0:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这样还什么都学不会
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的才能也就仅此而已
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会收他们为徒了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.53,0:11:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心的是
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的生命安全哎
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我修行的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.03,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可是在严冬的布里格斯山（Briggs）困了一个月哦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.03,0:11:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一般人哪能跟你比呀
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.83,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个岛上食物丰富
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定死不了啦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住啦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这个要怎么吃啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,咔嚓一刀
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,咔嚓…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦 还是哥哥你来吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只负责抓啦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,每次碰到麻烦你都丢给我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.73,0:12:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 站住
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.23,0:12:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,小狐狸
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是别吃肉改吃鱼吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可怎么才能抓到鱼呀
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没竿没线也没钩啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.73,0:12:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没有食物 也没有火
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.83,0:12:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别说啦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛呀 哥哥
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.03,0:13:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.53,0:13:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,呜哇 好酸
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我…还活着
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吃着蚂蚁而活着
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,吃掉生命而活着
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,活着
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.63,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们绝对不会死
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.73,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.33,0:14:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 还差一点点
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.63,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,成功啦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,明天就一个月啦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.33,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 「一即全 全即一」的答案找到了么
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.03,0:15:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想 但还是半懂不懂的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.63,0:15:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不是很确定…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.13,0:15:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你想 我肚子饿得发晕时不是吃了蚂蚁吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 吃了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,酸得要死
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时就想
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.33,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如果当时我没吃然后饿死了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定也会被狐狸或者蚂蚁吃掉吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,然后归于大地变成草
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然后被兔子吃掉
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是食物链啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不光如此
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.23,0:15:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这座小岛很久以前说不定沉睡在海底
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.63,0:15:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,过了几万年说不定就会变成山顶
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.03,0:15:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,世间万物都是相互联系的？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.73,0:16:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都处于看不见的洪流之中
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.83,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道这是不是就是宇宙或者世界
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.33,0:16:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在这样广阔的天地中
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟阿尔也和蚂蚁一样渺小
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只是洪流中的一小滴水
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,「全」中的「一」而已
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.93,0:16:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 这些渺小的「一」聚集在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,才能形成「全」
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}这个世界就是这样形成的…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,到了约定的日子了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.63,0:16:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,说说「一即全 全即一」的答案吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,「全」就是世界
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,「一」就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.43,0:16:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 开始正式修行吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒啦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.53,0:16:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,炼成阵的基础就是圆之力
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.83,0:16:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,圆显示力量的循环
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在圆上画出构成式
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以发动力量
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是力量的循环
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,（惊）
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,实际体验是最好的方法
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.63,0:17:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 在午饭准备好之前好好复习吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.83,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 圆显示力量的循环
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在圆上画出构成式
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.63,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以发动力量
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.63,0:17:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可是师父只是双手合十就可以炼成吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.73,0:17:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不用画出构成式也可以吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.93,0:17:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我本身就是类似构成式的存在了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样才可以做到呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看到真理之后也许就可以了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老师也见过真理
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.83,0:18:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要说什么
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.23,0:18:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然不用构成式就能炼成了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.23,0:18:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而且阿尔冯斯变成了空铠甲
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而你一只手一只脚是机械铠
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.03,0:18:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,师父 你怎么知道
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.43,0:18:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这点小事交过手就知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.53,0:18:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你也见到那个了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.63,0:19:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真是无可救药的一对师徒啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,师父也…见过那个吗
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.03,0:20:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们夫妇俩一直没有孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易怀上了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.73,0:20:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,却因为我生病
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.73,0:20:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的孩子没能活着降生
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.23,0:20:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我触犯了禁忌
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.53,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因此失去了部分内脏
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.13,0:20:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是个大傻瓜
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.93,0:20:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该早点告诉你们的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.83,0:20:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不会啦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们自作自受
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没觉得痛苦什么的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.03,0:20:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想着恢复身体以后要吃什么
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,反而很期待呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.93,0:20:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.53,0:20:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 就是
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.63,0:21:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这两个傻孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.43,0:21:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不必勉强自己了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.73,0:21:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.83,0:21:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.83,0:21:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.83,0:21:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.53,0:21:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.73,0:21:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.43,0:21:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界按照无法想象的大法则运转
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.13,0:21:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,只要知道这个法则
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.73,0:21:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,进行分析和重组
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.73,0:21:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是炼金术
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.93,0:21:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也是生命的法则
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.63,0:21:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,炼金术的基础 分解和重组
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟食物链一个道理
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.23,0:22:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了兔子就是将兔子的肉进行分解
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.43,0:22:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,重组为自己的身体
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.93,0:22:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,兔子也是把吃下去的草进行重组
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.23,0:22:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,炼金术就是生命本身啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:23:59.05,0:24:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沉迷于自己欲望的人
Dialogue: 1,0:24:01.95,0:24:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,其名为格利德
Dialogue: 1,0:24:04.35,0:24:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是敌人还是同伴
Dialogue: 1,0:24:05.95,0:24:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,出现在爱德等人面前的
Dialogue: 1,0:24:08.65,0:24:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛是为战斗而生的异形
Dialogue: 1,0:24:12.75,0:24:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 1,0:24:15.45,0:24:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 1,0:24:17.35,0:24:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,第13话 达布利斯的野兽们
Dialogue: 1,0:24:22.25,0:24:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,强者现身
